<!-- GTCC Capstone -->
<section id="GTCCCapstone">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center">

                <h2 class="section-heading" style="text-shadow:2px 2px 3px rgba(30,30,30,0.25)">GTCC Programming Capstone course</h2>
                <hr class="blue" />

                <p>The Programming Capstone course is a semester-long, on-line course with minimal instructor involvement. This course is the last course taken before graduation.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom:0px">The course is designed to replicate real-world business analysis and programming techniques, and begins with an introduction to a (fictitious) business, which includes interviews with key employees and samples of paper forms the business uses.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center">
                <div style="padding:10px; border:2px solid #009999; background-color:rgba(0,153,153,0.05)">
