                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>



        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center">
                <p style="margin-top:40px; margin-bottom:0px" >A SWOT (Strengths, Weaknesses, Opportunities, & Threats) analysis is performed to ensure the company's needs are understood. Next, database design is considered through the creation of an Entity Relationship Diagram (ERD).</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                <div style="padding:10px; border:2px solid #009999; background-color:rgba(0,153,153,0.05)">
