        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center">
                <p style="margin-top:40px">Database creation narrows the class focus to four key business processes:</p>
                <ul style="list-style:none; margin-top:-16px; padding-left:0px">
                    <li>Customer Maintenance</li>
                    <li>Employee & Inventory Maintenance</li>
                    <li>Inventory & Sales Transactions</li>
                    <li>Reports</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="margin-bottom:0px">Application development and documentation proceeds through the remainder of the semester, with each of the key areas being developed. Microsoft Access 2016 and Visual Studio 2012 were used in the creation of the C# Winforms-based application.</p>
            </div>
        </div>



